{"tid":291021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[街霸] 年輕人坐博愛座　被老伯騰空一夾夾爆你個頭","createTime":"2017-06-20T08:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T16:14:16.000Z","uid":19889,"like":394,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de9510c6612846866f95810ae2bc7e7c771676d9","tid":291021,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170620/640_e2531897f04fa4c2191b4108d396dce8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170620%2F640_e2531897f04fa4c2191b4108d396dce8.jpg&h=731501bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n博愛座的爭議不僅台灣有，國外亦然！近來兩張照片在韓國瘋傳，一名年輕人疑似搭公車時坐在博愛座上，結果被一名年約70歲左右的老伯騰空狠踢頭部。<br />\n據《kmib》網站指出，這名年輕人坐在博愛座上，不知道是否與站在旁邊的老伯起了突衝，老伯竟然抓著公車上方橫桿，整個人騰空雙腳往年輕人頭部踢去，年輕人幾乎跌落座位。<br />\n照片引發討論，有人認為年輕人佔據博愛座不應該，但也有反對聲音批評老伯暴力行為不可取，而且老伯動作也不需要坐博愛座。但其實當事雙方是否因為讓不讓座起衝突，並不確定。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170620/1144145/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170620%2F1144145%2F&d=6TMFAya9mM%2BOk1hvvrry28PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=41a3fd55\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170620/1144145/</a>"},{"pid":"31ed9b419881391136e94e151d733e96b9c1c4a6","tid":291021,"uid":19919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20d8ee2d71edfa79257779905360b02c346b1c4","tid":291021,"uid":22675,"like":31,"dislike":12,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"內地係共產中文！！係大陸啊！！"},{"pid":"97c43dac2c0a9486940f339f4822a5758c8ce082","tid":291021,"uid":113474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:37:22.000Z","msg":"凌空交剪腳一野夾爆你個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji